---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "I'm a starter theme for Astro.build",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
			Welcome. I am a multi-faceted IT professional with a deep passion for cybersecurity and network
			infrastructure. My goal is to leverage my expertise in both defensive and offensive security to
			build and protect robust, efficient, and secure digital environments. I thrive on solving
			complex technical challenges and am dedicated to sharing my knowledge and helping others
			navigate the complexities of IT.
		</p>
		<h3 class="!text-2xl">What I Do</h3>
		<p>
			My work focuses on the complete lifecycle of IT security and administration. I am driven by a
			proactive approach to security and a commitment to user support.
		</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				<strong>Penetration Testing & Security Audits:</strong> Identifying and mitigating
				vulnerabilities before they can be exploited.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Digital Forensics:</strong> Investigating security incidents to understand the scope
				and prevent future occurrences.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Secure Network Architecture:</strong> Designing and implementing secure, scalable
				network solutions using technologies like Cisco Meraki and VMware.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>System & Server Administration:</strong> Managing and hardening Windows and Linux
				environments, including Active Directory and server infrastructure.
			</li>
		</ul>
		<h3 class="!text-2xl">Core Competencies</h3>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>Network & Server Administration</li>
			<li>Network Security & Hardening</li>
			<li>Technical Troubleshooting</li>
			<li>Active Directory & VMware</li>
			<li>Kali Linux & Pentesting Tools</li>
			<li>IT Project Management</li>
		</ul>
		<h3 class="!text-2xl">Get In Touch</h3>
		<p>
			I am currently open to new full-time job opportunities and freelance projects. If you'd like
			to collaborate or discuss a role, please feel free to reach out.
		</p>
		<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@adjprodxn.ca" class="cactus-link">contact@adjprodxn.ca</a></p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
